Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:56.02,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}{\an7}{\pos(434,472)}38（t）坦克等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:56.02,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}{\an7}{\pos(132,540)}活用速度快的特點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:56.02,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}{\an7}{\pos(132,590)}以偵查為主要任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走攻守相當全面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為所有戰車主力的中型坦克
