Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:12:02.02,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}{\an7}{\pos(132,540)}走攻守均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:12:02.02,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}{\an7}{\pos(132,590)}是戰鬥的主力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支援中型坦克
